name: Sprint 100 Meter Dog Racing: Race Dogs On Tracks
name_original: Sprint 100 Meter Dog Racing: Race Dogs On Tracks
description:
Join the dog racing tracks for this greyhound and other racer dogd, these are pro greyhound racing tracks specially designed for 100 meter sprint racing, race to the fullest, race the maximum you can for the gold medal of 100 meter race.
knock out the opponents to win the title of Dog tracks racing. Gold medal is waiting for you.


Features

* Sprint racing tracks
* 100 meter racing model
* greyhounds and shephered dogs
